nodes.name: economy help
formdata:
Minecraft helper bot has an economy feature!
With the economy feature users can mine for money, and purchase mobs. The goal is to collect as many mobs as possible. If you want to add extra value to collecting mobs you can create special roles for people who have collected a certain amount of mobs! You can earn minecoins by either using mc!mine to mine a random number of minecoins you can earn 75-250 minecoins each time you mine. You can also earn minecoins just be being active! You earn 5 minecoins per message. Every message you send there is a 1 in 1000 chance of a mob spawner spawning, if you encounter a mob spawner you will be rewarded 30 mobs!
